{"tid":711563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2062年 中國會變成印度？","createTime":"2018-06-21T15:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T18:33:59.000Z","uid":71176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e07306f2c3f1e96c80fdf2c4dc68c6bcc922565a","tid":711563,"uid":71176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T15:45:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jeqH4eMGjhY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjeqH4eMGjhY&d=6Agar0zoNWVtdaUxWX%2Fl6ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=d95b7d58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jeqH4eMGjhY</a><br />\n係youtube見到呢條片 覺得幾有趣<br />\n大家唔好屌普通話住先<br />\n入面全部都係繁體中文字幕 睇字幕都可以<br />\n唔想睇嘅巴絲打 我呢到都有個小簡介<br />\n<br />\n內容係講話一個自稱2062未來人係日本論壇2ch到<br />\n兩次準確預測日本最大地震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分別係的3.11同熊本大地震<br />\n大家都對呢個未來人相當好奇<br />\n問咗唔少問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其中一條日本網民問未來人2062既問題<br />\n就係 2062年 中國會存在嗎？<br />\n2062答 不存在了 中國會變成印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然片主從下邊留言嘅網民都表示唔信<br />\n但係我就覺得好有可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個國家都慢慢步向文明<br />\n越係有知識嘅分子就越唔想生小朋友<br />\n得印度係咁生係咁生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地又點睇呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d104e27791e3c0b8fc847f1020fdb1da7fcee90b","tid":711563,"uid":190534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T15:48:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5d65f014bdff53ea99671b610caeffaa82ca166","tid":711563,"uid":71176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T16:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25a0db6fcbded53a1bb9b3a4b2d18db6c57c2a7","tid":711563,"uid":71176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T16:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1d784ceb51879ca06d23c9536754e7c73c1d83","tid":711563,"uid":144035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T16:56:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9182ef58da1584c5aa66f2498289bc6042a45943","tid":711563,"uid":71176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba1d784ceb51879ca06d23c9536754e7c73c1d83","tid":711563,"uid":144035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T16:56:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:13:22.000Z","msg":"意思係無左中國呢個國家 只有印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ca4dfd45b7910b76cdce67f9a80bd0f6ccbe10","tid":711563,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T18:33:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/023353_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F023353_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=41922ed0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}